Class CircularLinkedList<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • datastructures.AbstractList<E>
      • datastructures.CircularLinkedList<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<E>, java.util.Collection<E>, java.util.List<E>

    public class CircularLinkedList<E>
extends AbstractList<E>
    The circular Linked list is a list that is singly linked and circular. It is known to be the preffered list when implementing a Stack.
    Since:
    16-8-2014
    Version:
    20-8-2014
    Author:
